  "title": "⚡🌟 SALES ADVISOR – ENTRY LEVEL 🌟",
  "description": "<p>Training Provided | High Commission | Uncapped Earnings | Career Growth</p><p>💥 READY TO LAUNCH YOUR SALES CAREER?</p><p>If you want to:</p><p>Build real sales and communication skills</p><p>Earn performance-based, uncapped commissions</p><p>Grow quickly with a clear career path</p><p>Work in a supportive, energetic team environment</p><p>This opportunity is for you.</p><p>👤 WHO SHOULD APPLY</p><p>Fresh graduates ready to build skills</p><p>ORD personnel wanting a strong start</p><p>Career switchers looking for growth</p><p>Anyone with drive, positivity, and willingness to learn</p><p>No prior sales experience needed — we provide training.</p><p>🎯 WHAT YOU’LL DO</p><p>Connect with customers professionally</p><p>Understand and meet their needs</p><p>Present and promote products</p><p>Handle objections with confidence</p><p>Close sales and follow up effectively</p><p>🎓 TRAINING & SUPPORT</p><p>Comprehensive onboarding</p><p>Daily coaching and mentoring</p><p>Product knowledge and sales techniques</p><p>Feedback-driven improvement</p><p>💰 INCOME & REWARDS</p><p>Commission-based earnings</p><p>Unlimited earning potential</p><p>Incentives and travel rewards for top performers</p><p>🚀 CAREER PATH</p><p>Sales Advisor</p><p>Senior Advisor</p><p>Team Leader</p><p>Manager</p><p>Promotions based on performance and leadership.</p><p>🎉 TEAM CULTURE</p><p>Motivated and supportive environment</p><p>Team-building activities</p><p>Recognition and rewards</p><p>Experienced leaders guiding your growth</p><p>🚫 NOT FOR YOU IF</p><p>You want guaranteed fixed pay</p><p>You avoid challenges</p><p>You dislike performance-based roles</p><p>👉 CALL TO ACTION</p><p>🔥 DM “ADVISOR” or apply now!</p><p>🔥 Limited slots available</p><p>Start your sales journey today.</p>",
